            "name": "Attach Line",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The animated kite gives its line to an adjacent ally with a free hand. The kite remains attached until the creature releases it or the kite flies more than 60 feet away. A creature between them can also sever the line with a successful Strike against AC 13 that deals any amount of slashing damage.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
                  "alternate_type": "legacy",
                  "aonid": 104,
                  "game-obj": "Traits",
                  "type": "alternate_link"
